    "This is the application of common sense by the machine.",
    "All the predefined data is stored in the system, so whenever it needs action, it works automatically.",
    "This type of AI does not exist.",
    "involving simple decision making or exact computations to produce solutions.",
    "Here we are some few examples:  Genetic Algorithms: They are a specific methodology from the general field known as evolutionary computation, which is a branch of AI wherein proposed solutions to a problem adapt similarly as animal creatures adapt to their environments in real world."
